Time (Henry& Gizem system)
comment:
This is merely time. It is independent from the rest of the systems we are using. It\'s purpose is to   continuously increase in order to trigger an action from one of our nodes so that a disturbance will occur.

I will set TIME to increase in value by one second for 5 seconds, which I will tell the GLUCOSE to increase by 1 for 5 seconds simultaneously. This will produce a negative feedback from other systems to bring the value of blood GLUCOSE back down to it\'s normal value.
